===Reviews===
''The Aristocrats'' received a generally positive reception from film critics. Review aggregate website [[Rotten Tomatoes]] reports the film as holding a "Certified Fresh" rating, with an overall 80% positive approval rating based on 147 reviews, and a [[Weighted mean|rating average]] of 7.1 out of 10.<ref name="rotten" /> The site's general consensus is that the film is "Can a joke stand up to repeated tellings? Hilarious and revealing of the way comedy works, ''The Aristocrats'' demonstrates that it's possible."<ref name="rotten">{{cite news|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/aristocrats/ |title=The Aristocrats - Rotten Tomatoes |work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |year=2013 |accessdate=April 28, 2013|publisher=Flixter, Inc.}}</ref> At [[Metacritic]], which assigns a weighted mean rating out of 0–100 reviews from film critics, the film has a rating score of 72 based on 39 reviews, classified as a generally favorable reviewed film.<ref name="metacritic">{{cite news |title=The Aristocrats Reviews - Metacritic |work=[[Metacritic]]|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-aristocrats|accessdate=April 28, 2013|year=2013|publisher=CBS Interactive Inc.}}</ref>

